{"tid":1983046,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"6月期油續挫30% 特朗普研發放資金予油企 道指未止瀉跌500點","createTime":"2020-04-21T14:16:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T14:18:46.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"11cc5e0d7348357df4bc44c8409e86776b676ac8","tid":1983046,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/thC6Ue6m5FiN-hr8r8ZXyPix1Gs=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/46VLMZCDAEF7WJ6KOIYBA2VWME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FthC6Ue6m5FiN-hr8r8ZXyPix1Gs%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F46VLMZCDAEF7WJ6KOIYBA2VWME.jpg&h=d6251db8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際油價下挫，道指早段跌516點。<br />\n<br />\n國際油價繼續下挫，美股三大指數全線向下。道指早段跌516點或2.18%，報23134點；標指跌47點或1.67%，報2775點；納指跌96點或1.1%，報8476點。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普於Twitter上指：「我地絕對唔會令美國石油天然氣行業失望。我已經指示美國能源及財政部長制定一項為美國石油天然氣行業提供的資金援助計劃，長遠保住呢班咁重要嘅公司同就業。」（We will never let the great U.S. Oil &amp; Gas Industry down. I have instructed the Secretary of Energy and Secretary of the Treasury to formulate a plan which will make funds available so that these very important companies and jobs will be secured long into the future!）<br />\n<br />\n油價大崩圍持續，雖然期油正式轉倉，但6月紐約期油未有止跌迹象，最新跌30%至每桶14.3美元，而布蘭特期油亦跟隨跌23%至每桶19.66美元。另外，美國著名石油ETF「United States Oil Fund」亦急插約20%。<br />\n<br />\n恒指夜期跌172點，至23558點，低水236點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200421/Q4OLNJOZNBS55YSM7K2NLD4DPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200421%2FQ4OLNJOZNBS55YSM7K2NLD4DPY%2F&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8j1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=28ff974b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200421%2FQ4OLNJOZNBS55YSM7K2NLD4DPY%2F&h=d013ad54\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200421/Q4OLNJOZNBS55YSM7K2NLD4DPY/</a>"},{"pid":"243683ce15f69f6a4b253ccd135334a5907cfebc","tid":1983046,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:17:35.000Z","msg":"有排都唔使旨意，美國會理香港呢邊<br />\n<br />\n所以中共先咁越嚟越放肆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cacfaffca503a19f6704bf065b12bf2530d5b3ea","tid":1983046,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/peoSq06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpeoSq06.jpg&h=638f5202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j1aYmzs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj1aYmzs.jpg&h=02f446fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kti3xF8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkti3xF8.jpg&h=f65b9aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VDM8JNX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVDM8JNX.jpg&h=d22d7406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sh96vs0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsh96vs0.jpg&h=69abff0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WzcLL1n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWzcLL1n.jpg&h=6ce07bc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32T3xGo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32T3xGo.jpg&h=3d7fd808&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}